**How to Host a Game (everyone has to be on the same wifi)**
*Run the server before the network / clients*
*Make sure everyone is on the same wifi*
1. Enter your local IP adress into server veriable
2. enter a port number that is unused eg 5555
3. enter the ammount of players in the game into the playercap

**How to join a game**
1. Enter the local IP and port number of the server host
2. Run game in a terminal seperate to the server terminal (a dedicated terminal)
3. If running multiple players on the same sever use of the clients and run in a dedicated terminal
4. Wait for all players to fill the game